85 honoring and giving special tribute to America's 250th
86 birthday celebration and to all contributors in a manner
87 that will be remembered for a lifetime.
88 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, That copies of this
89 resolution be distributed to the ASF Foundation, Home of the
90 Alabama State Games.
